<title>ITALY: Autogrill owner to seek Milan listing.</title>
<headline>Autogrill owner to seek Milan listing.</headline>
<dateline>MILAN 1997-03-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shareholders of Schemaventidue Spa, the owner of Finanziaria Autogrill Spa, which in turn controls roadside restaurant chain Autogrill Spa, voted to request a listing on the Milan bourse.</p>
<p>The company said in a statement the request for a listing on the screen-based market would be lodged after the incorporation of Autogrill and Finanziaria Autogrill into Schema Ventidue had been completed.</p>
<p>Shareholders of the three companies are due to meet to approve the merger before the end of April 1997.</p>
<p>-- Milan newsroom +392-66102321</p>
